                      "ep_id": 3487,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/23/47826599/66a9dceb7daa0fd96ac32f3a9af48068_433031040499713868.png",
                      "name": "归终",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 51,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Xiao_icon.png",
                      "name": "魈",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3519,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/31/47826599/c11e8841d51eca4a0f5877567d0b1b28_6786782551800111802.png",
                      "name": "伐难",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3518,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/31/47826599/2a70abcd41f1c25b94da6c18901fc863_6939628724811528098.png",
                      "name": "弥怒",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3520,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/31/47826599/7280f8fc2afecab369f640ed8370390d_1746627869451140690.png",
                      "name": "应达",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 2314,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/book/Yakshas: The Guardian Adepti_icon.png",
                      "name": "护法仙众夜叉录",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "浮舍",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/31/157749474/bd3411f8ef5ac049d8e7a0fd615ca8f6_3817351730078456975.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "浮舍是岩王帝君召唤的第一个夜叉，他从岩王帝君那里获得了腾蛇太元帅的称号。住在天遒，是夜叉中的大哥，神魂强大。他生有四臂，操纵雷元素之力，不仅知道自己如何战斗，还知道如何带领其他人参加战斗。为此，他备受尊敬。浮舍最喜欢的技巧是引诱敌人并在意想不到的时刻攻击他。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "right",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/31/157749474/9a723eb62826da5b39b435eec28c8297_3323336895742752635.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "500年前发生了一场大灾难。深渊魔兽侵扰了提瓦特七国，璃月也不例外。为了让受伤的人民安全逃生，也为了维护他们在岩王帝君眼中的信用，千岩军在深渊中勇敢地与怪物战斗，突然，四臂夜叉出现在战场上。疯狂的他在关键时刻将魔兽的注意力引向了自己。千岩军与他一起深入深渊。他们使用法宝太威仪盘将自己和魔兽尽数困在层岩巨渊底部的空间内，最终以只有浮舍和伯阳生还的惨痛代价将全部魔兽消耗致死，但两人也再无法离开这片空间中。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/31/157749474/90ec28a7bc8d4e51d7db9d334bd6a40d_3195817803812823116.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "浮舍与夜兰的祖父伯阳一起落入时间本身被扭曲的层岩巨渊底部的空间。浮舍因为业障忘了自己的兄弟姊妹、忘了自己为何来到深渊，也忘了自己的名字。浮舍在神智不清时称伯阳为弥怒或金鹏，但他只是耐心地纠正了他。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "right",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/31/157749474/2af43f3c6bf7a6db5cd8c137c3585938_8064404638026797414.jpg"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "有一天，浮舍想起了自己是谁。他将自己的名字告诉了伯阳，但他们却始终没能离开这片空间。浮舍被困在层岩巨渊底部的空间，魈以及同行的旅行者众人了解到了浮舍与众千岩军在此抗击魔物的真相，并与浮舍的幻象短暂交手。创造太威仪盘的仙人将这件法宝交给凡人导致整件事的发生。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "相关词条：",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
